Articles.Content:
i use CKAN, except when i need to install mods that it doesn't have (volumetric clouds), i installed a few mods the other day, The VAB decided to just stop, nothing in the VAB worked after that (exept for the clicky sounds, which still is enough for a game but still), Does anyone know what is going on? The mods are from a video series (martincitopants "Kerbal Scuffed Program") played on 1.8, im on 1.12.5. Modlist:
